OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FThe NHS Borders CEO says its workforce
OL,7,Fare "fatigued" following a "really
OL,8,Fchallenging" period of winter
OL,9,Fpressures.
OL,11,FTen months after taking on the role of
OL,12,FChief Executive, Peter Moore says the
OL,13,Fhealth board will be launching a
OL,14,Fstrategy plan in two weeks setting out
OL,15,Fits vision for services.
OL,17,F"It's about re-engineering how we use
OL,18,Four resources and reorganise that to
OL,19,Fhelp meet the demand," he said.
