OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FThis February NHS Borders issued an
OL,7,Furgent appeal for medical
OL,8,Fprofessionals to work extra shifts to
OL,9,Fhelp tackle 'exceptional challenges'
OL,10,Fwith Borders General Hospital at
OL,11,Fcapacity earlier this year.
OL,13,FMr Moore believes the system is now
OL,14,F"coping really well" considering the
OL,15,Fsituation.
