OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FHe said: "I really recognise that our
OL,7,Fpressures extend across primary,
OL,8,Fcommunity and mental health services.
OL,9,FOur activities are broadly the same as
OL,10,Flast year and our performance is
OL,11,Fslightly up - it's not where we need
OL,12,Fto be - but I think we're in a decent
OL,13,Fposition going into the start of this
OL,14,Fyear. I really recognise we've got a
OL,15,Fbig performance challenge on our
OL,16,Fhands."
