OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FMr Moore said winter had been a
OL,7,Fdifficult period for staff, he added:
OL,8,F"I think the workforce are fatigued...
OL,9,Fit's been a long four or five months
OL,10,Fto work though and that has been
OL,11,Freally challenging across all aspects
OL,12,Fof the health board and we see that on
OL,13,Fa day-to-day basis.
OL,15,F"Part of addressing that fatigue is
OL,16,Facknowledging it, but also to be clear
OL,17,Fabout what's the vision for services
OL,18,Fin the future."
