OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FExclusive data obtained by
OL,7,FRepresenting Border using freedom of
OL,8,Finformation legislation shows 7% of
OL,9,FNHS Border's posts for consultants are
OL,10,Fvacant and most of these have been
OL,11,Funfilled for more than a year.
OL,13,F"You always want more staff but
OL,14,Fequally, it's about understanding the
OL,15,Fchallenges we have, we do have a
OL,16,Freally difficult financial envelope to
OL,17,Flive within," continued Mr Moore.
OL,19,F"I think part of our strategy going
OL,20,Fforward is about how we release more
OL,21,Fof our staff's time."
