OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FDiscussing the recruitment challenges
OL,7,Fin the area, Mr Moore said: "It's a
OL,8,Fconstraint on our waiting times... we
OL,9,Fdo have too long of a wait.
OL,11,F"We need to understand how we engage
OL,12,Fdifferently and appeal as an employer
OL,13,Fso we can attract roles in a different
OL,14,Fway.
OL,16,F"There's some geographical barriers. A
OL,17,Flot of the challenges of living in the
OL,18,FBorders is that it's far from the
OL,19,Fteaching hospitals in Edinburgh and
OL,20,FGlasgow."
