OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government has pledged
OL,7,Fthat no one will have to wait more
OL,8,Fthan a year for an operation from
OL,9,FMarch 2026.
OL,11,FPublic Health Scotland figures,
OL,12,Fcompiled by the charity Scotland
OL,13,FVersus Arthritis, show 136 patients in
OL,14,Fthe Borders have waited more than 12
OL,15,Fmonths for orthopaedic surgery.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
