OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,FMr Moore says the target set by
OL,7,Fministers "has to be achievable", he
OL,8,Fadded: "We take too much of our
OL,9,Fcommunities time to treat them when
OL,10,Fthey have a health need. We need to
OL,11,Faddress that in the strategy coming
OL,12,Fforward.
OL,14,F"To wait over a year does genuinely
OL,15,Fhave a big impact on people's
OL,16,Findependence and employment. What I
OL,17,Fhave been encouraged about is the
OL,18,FScottish Government's direction, that
OL,19,Fthis isn't something individual boards
OL,20,Fneed to face on their own.
