OL,3,CNHS Borders CEO says health care
OL,4,Cprofessionals are 'fatigued'
OL,6,F"There's a real collective approach
OL,7,Fabout how we do this in collaboration
OL,8,Fwith other boards.
OL,10,FI think there are always challenges
OL,11,Ffor rural and island boards and we do
OL,12,Fdeliver care in a slightly different
OL,13,Fway... I think our needs are being
OL,14,Fheard."
